                Iulio Aprili b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciario</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>c<expan><ex>o</ex><abbr>hort</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> I Asturum <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> XXII Cauru <lb n="4"/>Blendonis <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilia</ex></expan> <abbr>con</abbr> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iva</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ecit</ex></expan> et sibi
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): CIL 03, 04842: irrtümlich (vgl. CIL III 11508) eine Zeile vorangestellt mit dem Text &amp;quot;&amp;quot;Eludon[i] et&amp;quot;&amp;quot; und dem Kommentar &amp;quot;&amp;quot;Initio fractam esse nemo adnotavit&amp;quot;&amp;quot;. Material: Marmor aus Tentschach.</p>
            </div>
